{"tid":550304,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連住尼聽講佢今日生日 [shocking]","createTime":"2018-02-04T16:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T19:47:32.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4123bb6c435135d175bb2773940d8bdcda82c93b","tid":550304,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T16:00:06.000Z","msg":"是咁的，三十一年前，地球上出現左一隻生物...佢姓連，叫尼住<br />\n有陣時，佢都唔知自己其實係叫連尼住，定係連住尼<br />\n佢慢慢嘅長大，曾經...佢了解到自己嘅無力，不停嘅追求改變<br />\n佢已經知道自己時日無多，所以不停去迫自己 Be a better me<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/559747_601422503251429_1446742394_n.jpg?oh=45f706c84c2c2cbf520baf7a40aeef31&amp;oe=5AE11971\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F559747_601422503251429_1446742394_n.jpg%3Foh%3D45f706c84c2c2cbf520baf7a40aeef31%26oe%3D5AE11971&h=05d6cd61&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n霎眼三十一歲，雖然身邊不小人妒忌自己所有的<br />\n但仍舊自覺一事無成，自知什麼也做得不好<br />\n縱然努力過，很多東西也仍然得不著，徒費心力<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/234726_e136fe5566eaa8e3e5818988afeccc44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F234726_e136fe5566eaa8e3e5818988afeccc44.jpg&h=94cd1f96&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n人生當中有很多迷失，找不著方向的時間<br />\n當然，身為一個 Programmer，自己心中有一條冇得輸嘅 Formula<br />\n佢會仍然行落去，幾年前係呢一個地方，佢搵到自己嘅興趣<br />\n得到好多嘅肯定，難得係佢眾多錯敗當中，得到一眾連登仔嘅賞識<br />\n實在深感欣慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原文</span></strong></span><br />\n連住尼聽講佢今日生日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (5/2/2014 12:14)<br />\n發起人：連尼住<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/1044713_540241159369564_234350183_n.jpg?oh=751101ac6fe2a220feca7e0d122aad17&amp;oe=5B14CA71\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F1044713_540241159369564_234350183_n.jpg%3Foh%3D751101ac6fe2a220feca7e0d122aad17%26oe%3D5B14CA71&h=666bee13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4957491\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D4957491&d=%2By7rlLSItChSCEcL4xGf%2BF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=b5eac701\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4957491</a></div>"},{"pid":"90df387281a4c834bc89ddf6d31baf71ba4963aa","tid":550304,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T16:00:59.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"c9c7983e2e29a87a240524d4c7f345690f4b9ab1","tid":550304,"uid":55614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T16:01:05.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母呀<br />\n你老母比狗屌"},{"pid":"e3ec7e87c96f2f2d406227b10d23ef49967b79db","tid":550304,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c9c7983e2e29a87a240524d4c7f345690f4b9ab1","tid":550304,"uid":55614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T16:01:05.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母呀<br />\n你老母比狗屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T16:02:01.000Z","msg":"冇連登你仲上緊香討咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3738a8eda4663988fdb6c7ef8fb19649f4d5d475","tid":550304,"uid":59987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T16:03:29.000Z","msg":"叫佢食屎喇能樣，同孌童變態佬agentcc一伙既仆街"},{"pid":"d6009d2f3ff891d7f37917936ddd49827f880fc9","tid":550304,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T16:04:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>網民回應</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/0